links.title: $COP Marimaca Copper Receives Environmental Approval for Upcoming Drilling Program
links.description: VANCOUVER, British Columbia, Nov. 05, 2020 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Marimaca Copper Corp. ("Marimaca Copper" or the "Company") (TSX: MARI) is pleased to announce that the Antofagasta Environmental Evaluation Commission has approved, by a majority vote, the Company's new exploration campaigns, which will encompass further drilling at the Marimaca Oxide Deposit ("MOD"), exploration drilling at the Marimaca Sulphide Target and in the broader Marimaca District.
